videos.headline: Sullivan scoops and scores for a Georgia State TD
videos.description: Chandon Sullivan recovers the fumble and scores a touchdown after Georgia Southern's Myles Campbell coughs it up.

videos.headline: Georgia Southern's Campbell redeems himself with rushing TD
videos.description: Myles Campbell speeds to the end zone for a 12-yard rushing touchdown to tie the game 7-7.

videos.headline: Werts takes it to the house for an Eagles TD
videos.description: Shai Werts 5-yard rushing touchdown keeps Georgia Southern ahead 17-7.

videos.headline: Manning fires to Carter for Georgia State TD
videos.description: Conner Manning finds Roger Carter for a 4-yard touchdown late in the third quarter.

videos.headline: Manning's pass picked off by Georgia Southen's  DeLaRosa
videos.description: Conner Manning's pass is intercepted by Chris DeLaRosa and returned for 15 yards.

videos.headline: Georgia State's Traylor scoops up the fumble
videos.description: James Traylor recovers the fumble and rushes 5 yards after Georgia Southern loses the ball.

videos.headline: Georgia State takes back the lead with passing TD
videos.description: Conner Manning finds an open Penny Hart for a 9-yard touchdown pass to put the Panthers' ahead 21-17.
